Tuition
To be eligible for the early bird discounted rate , full payment must be received by 11 November 2015 .
Early_Bird_Rate : 2,600 USD ( see cut off dates for your chosen training , above ) . No exceptions .
Standard_Rate : 2,800 USD
In order for Suzanne to maintain a high level of personal attention for each trainee , spaces are limited .
If you would like to pay in 2 instalments , a 50% deposit holds your place and the remaining 50% must be paid 30 days prior to the start date of the training . Sign ups 30 days in advance or less , must be paid in full .
GROUPS_OF 3 OR_MORE_STUDENTS signing up and paying at once receive a 10% discount off the regular price of the course .
There are no refunds for this course , but if you become unable to attend your selected course , you are welcome to attend from a later date or use tuition towards another training course . If_Suzanne cancels for any reason , a full refund will be given .
This is a globally recognized training , accredited with the Worldwide_Yoga_Alliance .
